 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 对…担心 
 -- I'm apprehensive about moving to Japan; I have never lived abroad before.
 -- 我对移居日本感到担心; 我以前从未在国外生活过。
 
be armed to the teeth v expr figurative (have many weapons)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 武装到了牙齿 wǔ zhuāng dào le yá chǐ  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 全副武装 wǔ zhuāng dào le yá chǐ，quán fù wǔ zhuāng TC Traditional Chinese 全副武裝 
