           --> SC Simplified Chinese 用...全副武装  
 
be arsed vi + adj UK, vulgar, slang (willing to make effort)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 愿意的 yuàn yì de TC Traditional Chinese 願意的  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 乐意的 yuàn yì de ，lè yì de TC Traditional Chinese 樂意的 
 -- 备注 : Used in the negative, in questions, or when there is doubt.
 -- I asked him to check it for me but he said he couldn't be arsed.
 
