           --> SC Simplified Chinese 别害怕 bié hài pà  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 勇敢点 bié hài pà，yǒng gǎn diǎn 
 -- You have to be a man about this, and admit that you made a mistake.
 
be a man v expr (male: reach adulthood)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 成年，成人，长成男子汉 chéng nián ，chéng rén TC Traditional Chinese 成年，成人  (男子)
 -- Dan's young son wants to be an astronaut when he is a man.
 
