           --> SC Simplified Chinese 告知 gào zhī  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 使...知晓 
 -- We need to make sure all team members are across these changes.
 
be adhered to vi (not be deviated from)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 遵守，遵循 zūn shǒu，zūn xún TC Traditional Chinese 遵守，遵循  
 -- These rules and regulations must be adhered to at all times, or you will face discharge.
 
