           --> SC Simplified Chinese 有冲突  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 相抵触 
 -- The defendant was well aware that in accepting the bribe, he was afoul of the law.
 -- 被告很清楚，他接受贿赂的行为是违法的。
 
