Be serious! Be as serious as him!

be unable to accommodate

Because of overpopulation, the business world is going to be more and more competitive

Better to be the head of a chicken than the tail of a pheonix

but never be afraid to try new things

can be negotiated

Can rendaku be explained by Chinese pronunciation?

can use, can't use, can be used, can't be used

can't be named on the same day

Cantonese: Will you be coming on Wednesday?

Christmas won't be the same this year (because of COVID).

do you consider yourself to be the speaker of a dialect?

Don't be such a princess

Don't think, feel. Be water, my friend  (Bruce Lee)



